s dairy line mr cawley also tried to a defense verdict the first strategic litigation against public participation “slapp” lawsuit tried in the commonwealth of pennsylvania finally mr cawley has counseled and litigated consumer credit matters for lenders including issues arising under the equal credit opportunity act and has addressed other compliance issues dealing with federal and state laws governing consumer credit mr cawley is av rated by marindale hubbel was awarded  outstanding educator of the year in  by the insurance society of philadelphia is a subcommittee chair for the american bar associations insurance coverage litigation committee iclc a member of iadc and is on the insurance committee for the union league of philadelphia tweets by acilegal latest blog posts hear from top fda regulatory experts at aci’s th annual fda boot camp devices edition pharmaceuticals  biotech  life sciences by american conference institute  jun  0 aci’s fda boot camp to feature a “who’s who” of the fda regulatory bar pharmaceuticals  biotech  life sciences by american conference institute  jun  0 highlights of keynote address at aci’s brazil summit on anticorruption anticorruption  fcpa by american conference institute  may  0 law0 highlights aci pto proceedings ptab judges roundtable intellectual property by american conference institute  may  0 aci’s pto proceedings covered by law0 intellectual property by american conference institute  may  0 view conferences by location by sector featured view cart continue shopping close michael cawley ryanair holdings plc profile  biography  bloomberg feedback michael cawley former codeputy ceocoo ryanair holdings plc career history codeputy ceocoo ryanair holdings plc 00 deputy ceocoo ryanair ltd 00 cfodircommercial ryanair holdings plc 00 finance director gowan group ltd  show more website wwwryanaircom corporate information address airside business park swords ireland phone  fax  web url wwwryanaircom from the web personal information